In 2021, millions of people are playing Sudoku games. They are constantly training their brains through Sudoku games. In 2022, there will be more than ten million people training their brains through Sudoku games. Are you ready?
This is a Free Sudoku game, which contains a number of difficulty levels, each level is specially designed, there are simple, but also burn brain, to help you grow from a novice Sudoku master, your brain will become more sensitive.
This game also contains a daily challenge, so that you have different puzzles in your daily challenge, making you smarter and more flexible.
In addition to the level challenge mode, there is also endless mode, through which you can carry out different challenges. Very suitable for beginners and advanced players of the classic Sudoku. Whether you want to relax or keep your mind active - pass the time in a pleasant way!
This is a leisure puzzle Sudoku game, which not only allows you to pass the time, but also makes your thinking more flexible and active in the fragmented time. If you insist on playing for a period of time, I believe you will grow up.
In the game, you can identify each uncertain number, you can also click a number, so that you can clearly see the location of each same number, when you really can't reason out, you can also use prompt props.
Seemingly simple numbers, which contains infinite thinking, careful logic, the fun of solving problems, can be reflected in this Sudoku game, you also quickly try to experience the charm of numbers!
We will add more game modes later, such as 4x4 and 6x6, please look forward to it.
We hope you like the puzzle Sudoku game. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us.
Contact email :sairlen@qq.com
You can follow us on YouTube. We have new games that will be released on YouTube for the first time.
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjUfHcmBQ63JPpWvDdoCT9A
Thank you for your participation!
About Sudoku
Sudoku is a mathematical game originated from Switzerland in the 18th century. It is a logic game using paper and pen to calculate. Players need to follow 9 × According to the known numbers on the 9 disk, infer the numbers of all the remaining spaces, and ensure that the numbers in each row, column, and thick line Palace (3 * 3) contain 1-9, without repetition.
Sudoku disk is a nine palace, each palace is divided into nine small grid. In this 81 grid, given a certain number and problem-solving conditions, using logic and reasoning, fill in the other spaces with 1-9 numbers. Make 1-9 each number appear only once in every row, column and palace, so it is also called "nine palace grid".
This is a simple and elegant interface of leisure puzzle Sudoku game, a variety of difficulties, different levels, as well as daily challenge play, very suitable for you to exercise your brain, improve your reasoning ability. No matter how complicated the words are, they can't explain the charm of Sudoku. Please try it quickly! Hope you like it!

With Viggle’s new LIVE feature, you can act, talk, dance, and stream as anyone you want. Just upload an image and watch your character mirror your real-time body movements and facial expressions — perfect for roleplay, livestreaming, or going viral.

You’ve already seen Viggle all over social media — from the Joker/Lil Yachty walkout, to the “Dance if you can join” trend, AI photo dances, and the AI football wave on TikTok. Now it’s your turn to create the next viral moment.

Let Viggle bring fun to your life
- Be Anyone here. Take a break from daily life. Become your favorite character from a game, show, or something from your imagination. Talk, act, dance, and connect with others — as them. Every role reveals a part of you. 
- Make hilarious unexpected videos of you and your friends. Step into wild and never-imagined scenarios: score a game-winning goal, land an NBA-style dunk, recreate TikTok trends in one tap, rap like a real badass, even act alongside your favorite movie star...all made possible with Viggle. 
- Recreate iconic scenes for your favorite characters. Perfect for fandom. 

What you can do with Viggle's powerful features
- Live: Transform into anyone live. Record your roleplay, dance, or acting and share on socials to go viral, or stream directly to Twitch, YouTube, or Kick. All you need is one image and your camera — your character will move and express like you in real time.
- Mix: Replace anyone in a video. Upload one image and one video (or choose from our 5000+ fun templates). See you and your friends appear in crazy scenes doing impossible things. 
- Multi: Replace different characters in any video. Best for playing with your friends together or recreate a new senario for your favorite characters. 
- Mic: Advanced lip-syncing. Select music, type words, or record yourself, let your character talk, sing, dance, and move, all at once. 
- Rap: Make your photo rap. 
- Content feed: see what the community is creating. Remix, react, and create your own viral chain. 

Support and Community 
Reach out to us at support@viggle.ai or leave feedback on our website and Discord community.
Enjoy Viggle, where you can become anyone.

الا صلاتي تطبيق محاني يعرض اوقات الصلاة
الآن تستطيع سماع الاذان كاملا عند كل صلاة

هذا التطبيق يعرض أوقات الصلاة، القبلة بوصلة الاتجاه، التاريخ الهجري، مواقيت منبه الصلاة، حدث في مثل هذا اليوم، حديث اليوم، دعاء اليوم، بالاضافة لحكمة اليوم لكبار المسلمين كل هذه الميزات في هذا التطبيق الرائع،

حساب أوقات الصلاة
 بإستخدام نظام تحديد الموقع يقوم التطبيق بعرض أوقات الصلاة (الفجر، الشروق، الظهر، العصر، المغرب، العشاء) بالاضافة لحساب الوقت المتبقي للصلاة القادمة

 تستطيع اختيار المدينة يدويا من خلال صفحة البحث اذا كنت لا تريد ان تستخدم نظام تحديد المواقع

 بمجرد فتح التطبيق تجد شاشة عرض رائعة  تعرض لك اوقات الصلاة والوقت المتبقي  للصلاة القادمة والتاريخ الهجري والميلادي واسم المدينة المتواجد بها حاليا.

وبعد بحث مطول في كتب التاريخ الاسلامي تم اضافة خاصية حدث في مثل هذا اليوم الذي يظهر لك الاحداث والمناسبات بالنسبة للتاريخ الهجري وتستطيع مشاركتها مع من تريد 

تم ايضا اضافة حديث اليوم حيث تم اختيار مئات الاحاديث التي تحفزك للقراء والتمعن بالسنة النبوية كلما فتحت التطبيق

وتم اختيار ادعية منوعة من الكتاب والسنة ايضا سيتم اظهار دعاد جديد في كل مرة تفتح التطبيق وتستطيع مشاركته بصورة رائعة ومميزة

اصوات الآذان تم اختيار افضل الاصوات  واجملها والآذان الكامل عند كل صلاة دون الحاجة لفتح التطبيق فقط في هذا التطبيق متوفرة

القبلة: في مكان كنت ولا تعرف اتجاه القبلة هذه الميزة ستسهل عليك ذلك من خلال دون اي جهد بضل بوصلة القبلة ورسم الخرائط الذي يحدد موقعك واتجاهك بالنسبة للكعبة المشرفة، ويمكنك ايضا معرفة المسافة التي تفصلك عنها،
ساعة آبل: تستطيع معرفة وقت الصلاة القادمة والوقت المتبقي لها، من خلال الساعة دون الحاجة لفتح التطبيق،
مشاركة التطبيق مع من تريد من اصدقاء والعائلة

الاذان الكامل عند كل صلاة دون الحاجة لفتح التطبيق 

 تعديل أوقات الصلاة بما يناسب المنطقة المتواجد بها بكل سهولة

Inspire your children to uncover their unique interests
Help your children explore video content that they love and that parents trust, in an app made just for children. With easy navigation tools and a suite of features, you can help your children spend time online uncovering new interests, unleashing their imagination and building their confidence in their own unique world.

Help your children grow at their own pace
Your children are unique, so they should only see content that they're ready to explore. Decide what videos will help them make the most of their time online, then personalise individual profiles using custom content filters as they grow.

– Help your youngest children learn their ABCs, nurture their curiosity and more in 'Preschool' mode.
– Expand your children's interests to songs, cartoons or DIY crafts in 'Younger' mode.
– Give your older children the freedom to search popular music and gaming videos in 'Older' mode.
– Or, hand-pick the videos, channels and collections that your children can see in 'Approved content only' mode.

Rewatch videos and bond over favourites
Quickly find your children's favourite videos and the content that you've shared with them in the 'Watch it again' tab.

Shape your children's viewing experience with parental controls
Parental control features help you limit what your children watch, and better guide their viewing experience. Our blocking process aims to help keep videos on YouTube Kids family-friendly and safe – but each family's preferences are unique. Don't like a video or channel, or see inappropriate content? Flag it for our team to review.

Set a screen-time limit
Encourage your children to take a break in between exploring content. Use the 'Timer' feature to freeze the app when screen time is up so that your children can apply their new skills to the real world.

See important information
– Parental setup is needed to ensure the best experience for your family.
– Children may see commercial content from YouTube creators that are not paid ads.
– See the Privacy Notice for Google Accounts managed with Family Link for information on our privacy practices for signing in with a Google Account.
– If your children use the app without signing in with their Google Account, the YouTube Kids Privacy Notice applies.
